{"tid":1437082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民意民意民意！！！派傳單、放映會、連儂牆、記者會、air drop、長輩圖、網上文宣、電台phone-in全面進場！！！","createTime":"2019-08-09T12:22:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T20:30:39.000Z","uid":36592,"like":69,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"584400df4883a7ebbb26a878f9748cfe7725edd2","tid":1437082,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T12:22:05.000Z","msg":"港共變陣，全方位爭取民意手段要全面進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n派傳單，放映會，連儂牆，記者會，air drop，長輩圖，網上文宣，電台phone-in各有各做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n網上文宣除左連登仲要擴展到FB各大群組，BK，YouTube<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n脫離同溫層，不要圍爐取暖，係時候全面爭取民意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n堅持五大訴求，缺一不可，手足加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">一、徹底撤回修例\n二、收回暴動定義\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選</code></pre><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"407f814d59e6bd939d3e224f65c498155273133f","tid":1437082,"uid":36592,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T12:22:48.000Z","msg":"民意戰係好撚緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請全力推所有文宣行動post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9815b839a40665dee31416d5147c51cc5e1accf8","tid":1437082,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T12:23:25.000Z","msg":"民意戰係好撚緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請全力推所有文宣行動post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3349990c480b380e09a307852f456da668eec1e4","tid":1437082,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T12:25:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我建議文宣方向<br />\n<br />\n針對警方無差別襲擊，標籤為<span style=\"color: red;\">國家恐怖主義武裝組織</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n佢標籤我地做港獨，我地標籤返佢做「國家恐怖主義份子」 正名標籤警方為非法嘅武裝組織<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1426058\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1426058</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">認同請聯署請分享</span><br />\n已有30,969個簽名（9 Aug 2019 at 20:25）<br />\n［白宮聯署］香港警察為恐怖組織<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1427701\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1427701</a><br />\n<br />\n鼓勵遊行示威口號<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\nHKPF IS STATE TERRORIST!<br />\nNO STATE TERRORISM!<br />\nNO INDISCRIMINATE ATTACK!<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"0c4d33779f06b5eecd40397447bc0f0ba0e4e906","tid":1437082,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T12:25:36.000Z","msg":"民意戰係好撚緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請全力推所有文宣行動post<img src=\"/asse